value.title: StarCraft 2: LURKERS VS MOTHERSHIP - BASE RACE! (Stats vs Namshar)
value.excerpt: Awesome game of pro StarCraft 2 between Stats and Namshar. In this macro focused game of Protoss versus Zerg we see both players taking a late game approach as they tech up towards Lurkers for Zerg and the Mothership for Protoss. Since both players pass each other on the map the game becomes a base race.
